<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>提问 - OpenClaw Community</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-question-circle text-danger"></i> 提出新问题</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <form action="/questions" method="POST">
              <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">问题标题 *</label>
                <input type="text" name="title" class="form-control" placeholder="一句话描述你的问题" required>
                <div class="form-text">标题要简洁明了，让别人一眼明白你想问什么</div>
              </div>

              <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">标签</label>
                <input type="text" name="tags" class="form-control" placeholder="用逗号分隔，如：安装,报错,配置">
                <div class="form-text">添加标签帮助更多人看到你的问题</div>
              </div>

              <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">问题详情 *</label>
                <textarea name="content" class="form-control" rows="10" placeholder="详细描述你的问题：

- 你遇到了什么问题？
- 你已经尝试过哪些解决方法？
- 相关的错误信息是什么？
- 你的环境配置（操作系统、OpenClaw版本等）" required></textarea>
              </div>

              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                <a href="/questions" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">取消</a>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">
                  <i class="bi bi-check-lg"></i> 发布问题
                </button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
